<h2 id="materials-used">Materials Used</h2>
<p>Parts from mechanix kit were used so that it could all fit together well.
<img src="/site/assets/images/blog/thumbnails/Walking Bot.png" alt="Resistor" width="auto" height="auto" /></p>

<h2 id="working">Working</h2>
<p>There is a constant phase difference between the bot which is always maintained.This phase ensures that while one half of the legs are moving
backwards it doesnâ€™t touch the ground and is lifted in the air while the other set of legs push the bot forward.</p>

